descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 3 potential female followers. All of these followers can be found chillin' on the boardwalks of Riften (around and about the fishery).

The followers haven't been tweaked or balanced properly for any specialization, before I start working on that, I would very much first like to know the mod even works...

Note:
I'm completely uncertain as to the functionality of this mod, it would be my first mod and it is -for now at least- merely an experimental version.
